    <title>Linux操作一览</title>
    <url>/15/Linux%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%80%E8%A7%88/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="Linux"><a href="#Linux" class="headerlink" title="Linux"></a>Linux</h1><h2 id="linux-常用命令"><a href="#linux-常用命令" class="headerlink" title="linux 常用命令"></a>linux 常用命令</h2><figure class="highlight txt"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ls  -- 展开目录 </span><br><span class="line">ls -a -- 包括隐藏文件</span><br><span class="line">ls /usr -- 针对根目录查看当前usr下文件目录</span><br><span class="line">ll -- 展开目录并显示文件等的信息</span><br><span class="line">pwd -- 显示当前目录</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">cd / -- 回到根目录</span><br><span class="line">cd 或 cd ~ -- 用户目录 /root  -- 系统管理员 超级权限者的用户主目录</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">mkdir folder -- 创建文件夹 单个</span><br><span class="line">mkdir -p shell/folder  多个</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">touch service.js -- 创建文件</span><br><span class="line">cat service.js -- 查看文件内容</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">rm -f  -- 删除文件</span><br><span class="line">rm -rf -- 遍历强制删除任何文件 *包括空文件夹</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">vim shell.js -- 编辑文件 (没有会自创建)</span><br><span class="line">vi  shelljs -- 基本同上</span><br><span class="line">二者区别：</span><br><span class="line">1.vim 具有程序编辑的能力，可以以字体颜色辨别语法的正确性，方便程序设计；</span><br><span class="line">  2.vim可以当作vi的升级版本，他可以用多种颜色的方式来显示一些特殊的信息</span><br><span class="line">  3.vim里面加入了很多额外的功能，例如支持正则表达式的搜索、多文件编辑、块复制等等</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="网络端口状况"><a href="#网络端口状况" class="headerlink" title="网络端口状况"></a>网络端口状况</h2><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 查看tcp端口是否被占用</span></span><br><span class="line">netstat -nultp</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 过滤选择查看某个端口</span></span><br><span class="line">netstat -anp | grep 8000</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="进程状况"><a href="#进程状况" class="headerlink" title="进程状况"></a>进程状况</h2><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 查看所有进程</span></span><br><span class="line">ps -ef 或者 ps uat -- 区别在于展示风格不同</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 过滤查看mysql进程</span></span><br><span class="line">ps -ef | grep process(eg.mysql)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 查看某个进程的pid</span></span><br><span class="line">pgrep process(eg.mysql)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 杀掉某个进程</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">kill</span> -s 9 pid(eg.12485)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="Yum操作"><a href="#Yum操作" class="headerlink" title="Yum操作"></a>Yum操作</h2><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 安装</span></span><br><span class="line">yum install -y package(eg.ngnix)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 移除单个或者多个</span></span><br><span class="line">yum remove wget unzip -y</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="Iptables防火墙问题"><a href="#Iptables防火墙问题" class="headerlink" title="Iptables防火墙问题"></a>Iptables防火墙问题</h2><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 让在安全组配置中的端口可以访问</span></span><br><span class="line">iptables -I INPUT -p tcp -m state --state NEW -m tcp --dport 8087 -j ACCEPT</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="压缩解压文件"><a href="#压缩解压文件" class="headerlink" title="压缩解压文件"></a>压缩解压文件</h2><h3 id="zip"><a href="#zip" class="headerlink" title="zip"></a>zip</h3><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 压缩</span></span><br><span class="line">zip -r demo.zip demo</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 解压xxx.zip 到当前目录</span></span><br><span class="line">unzip xxx.zip -d . </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="tar"><a href="#tar" class="headerlink" title="tar"></a>tar</h3><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 压缩</span></span><br><span class="line">tar zcvf demo.tar.gz demo</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 解压</span></span><br><span class="line">tar -xvf demo.tar</span><br><span class="line">tar -xvf demo.tar.gz</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="链接远程服务器"><a href="#链接远程服务器" class="headerlink" title="链接远程服务器"></a>链接远程服务器</h2><ol>
<li>Mac<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ ssh root@119.23.208.xx </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
</ol>
<h2 id="文件上传下载"><a href="#文件上传下载" class="headerlink" title="文件上传下载"></a>文件上传下载</h2><h3 id="windos"><a href="#windos" class="headerlink" title="windos"></a>windos</h3><ol>
<li><p>安装<code>lrzsz</code></p>
<figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 安装</span></span><br><span class="line">yum install lrzsz -y</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 验证</span></span><br><span class="line">rpm -qa | grep lrzsz</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
<li><p>上传</p>
<figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">rz</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
<li><p>下载</p>
<figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sz xxx</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
</ol>
<h3 id="mac"><a href="#mac" class="headerlink" title="mac"></a>mac</h3><ol>
<li><p>上传</p>
<figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 基于本地终端操作 默认上传到目录为用户目录 如下：我用户目录存在test文件夹</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 上传文件</span></span><br><span class="line">scp  docker.md root@119.23.208.253:./test/docker.md</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 上传文件夹 xxx为某个文件夹</span></span><br><span class="line">scp -r xxx root@119.23.208.253:./</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
<li><p>下载</p>
<figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 基于本地终端</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 下载文件</span></span><br><span class="line">scp root@119.23.208.253:/root/docker.md .</span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 下载文件夹test</span></span><br><span class="line">scp -r root@119.23.208.253:/root/test .</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
</ol>
<h2 id="Mysql相关"><a href="#Mysql相关" class="headerlink" title="Mysql相关"></a>Mysql相关</h2><p>暂附参考链接：<a href="https://www.cnblogs.com/baoshu/p/centos-mysql.html">https://www.cnblogs.com/baoshu/p/centos-mysql.html</a></p>
<ol>
<li>查找是否已经安装了mysql<figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">rpm -qa | grep -i mysql</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
<li>连接mysql服务<figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mysql -u root -p</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
<li>进入到mysql控制台<ul>
<li>查看数据库服务器中的所有数据库： show databases;</li>
<li>查看正在使用的数据库：select database();</li>
<li>切换数据库： use database 数据库名称;</li>
<li>查看当前数据库中的所有表：show tables;</li>
<li>查看当前表的字段描述 desc table名;</li>
<li>增删改查和写sql语句查询一致。<ul>
<li>select * from table名<br>参考：<a href="https://www.cnblogs.com/1906859953Lucas/p/10925511.html">https://www.cnblogs.com/1906859953Lucas/p/10925511.html</a></li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ol>
]]></content>
